Ex-BASF Chief Hambrecht Says Nuclear Exit Costly, Bild Reports

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-05-31T05:13:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/ex-basf-chief-hambrecht-says-nuclear-exit-costly-bild-reports.html
Juergen Hambrecht, former chief
executive officer of  BASF SE (BAS) , said  Germany ’s planned exit from
nuclear power will be an “enormous effort” which will cost a
lot of money and jeopardize the country’s climate-protection
goals,  Bild  newspaper said, citing an interview with Hambrecht.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in  Frankfurt  at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 